# API Configuration
# For local development, use localhost
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:5000/api

# For mobile/network access, replace localhost with your PC's IP address
# Example: NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://192.168.1.100:5000/api
# To find your IP on Windows: ipconfig (look for IPv4 Address)
# To find your IP on Mac/Linux: ifconfig or ip addr show

# Instructions:
# 1. Copy this file to .env.local
# 2. Replace localhost with your PC's IP address if accessing from mobile
# 3. Restart the Next.js dev server after making changes

